  Source:
    Title: Young India
    Editor: M. K. Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 20 Dec 1928
---
I can give my own testimony and say that a heartfelt prayer is undoubtedly
the most potent instrument that man possesses for overcoming cowardice
and all other bad old habits. Prayer is an impossibility without a living
faith in the presence of God within.
